                                </svg>
                            </a>

                        </h4>
                   
                        <p style="color:#111112;">
                            I'm an online instructor , I built up my expertise thanks to years of experience with startups and investments, and I'm using the scientific method in business in order to find innovative approaches and doing a lot of research to uncover winning patterns among the most successful companies in the world.
                        </p>


                        <p style="color:#286099;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold">
                            <i class="bi bi-play-circle-fill"></i>
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="15" height="15" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-play-circle-    fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0M6.79 5.093A.5.5 0 0 0 6 5.5v5a.5.5 0 0 0 .79.407l3.5-2.5a.5.50    00   0-.814z" />
                            </svg>
                             Courses
                        </p>

                        <div style="box-shadow: rgba(50, 50, 93, 0.25) 0px 50px 100px -20px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 30px 60px -30px, rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.35) 0px -2px 6px 0px inset; margin-left:10px;padding:10px;color:black;">
                            <ul>
                            @foreach(var item in Model.Courses)
                            {
                                <li>@item.Title</li>
                                <hr />
                            }
                            </ul>

                        </div>



                       
                        
                            

                     </div>     

                    </div>
                </main>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>



 
